{"tid":728804,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【激罕】林穎彤紅色水着晒線騷腿","createTime":"2018-07-04T04:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T06:50:43.000Z","uid":117837,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ba3ed3ebcfbdce94e269de7d5365c71daec9d5ac","tid":728804,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:46:14.000Z","msg":"藝人林穎彤（Bella）好少甫水着照，不過皇天不負有心人，今日終於等到喇！Bella晒出兩張相，見佢着上一身紅色綁帶泳裝，大騷事業線同美腿，佢留言：「對上一次在ig發泳衣照應該是兩年多前的事&hearts;️從來沒穿過紅色泳衣 一直想試穿這種復古高腰設計的&hearts;️很喜歡😍這個夏天都只穿它好了！」連佢自己都話有成兩年冇甫過泳衣照，相信網民睇到今次呢個福利應該好感動。<br />\n<br />\n睇番啲相，Bella似乎浸緊溫泉，佢拎住車厘子擺甫士兼嘟嘴賣萌，網民即刻留言大讚「so hot」，仲有人話佢好弗好可愛，被佢秒殺呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180703/photo/bkn-20180703122235187-0703_00862_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180703%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180703122235187-0703_00862_001_01b.jpg&h=9fe745da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等足兩年先等到Bella甫泳衣相！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180703/photo/bkn-20180703122235187-0703_00862_001_02b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180703%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180703122235187-0703_00862_001_02b.jpg&h=a66a791f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n件泳衣嘅設計好靚喎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180703/photo/bkn-20180703122235187-0703_00862_001_03b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180703%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180703122235187-0703_00862_001_03b.jpg&h=b1116d5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身材都幾有睇頭㗎～<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180703/bkn-20180703122235187-0703_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180703%2Fbkn-20180703122235187-0703_00862_001.html&d=MNrG5JtwMuDYEPeFXOW5Bl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=6411e6a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180703/bkn-20180703122235187-0703_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4947633832be6e434e68ba2e42c4ea37eb7f1830","tid":728804,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:48:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63d6ab2c7ec57eea9fda76b0e037a1c86183bf0b","tid":728804,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d99cb3ff870c0d20986a3bc7974e42dffe03a67","tid":728804,"uid":144784,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"紅色嘅阿婆底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0ea4eadc4b50f90c309316df86c78591adb76a","tid":728804,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e41758a73a7698abd45ad423e6ad1c69bbc765","tid":728804,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:50:46.000Z","msg":"包臉正啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7029bd7c2414b75f0002b32ffffdc335248ea9b","tid":728804,"uid":121973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:51:33.000Z","msg":"成個杯緣子咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80464555231059ea588b63d1864563e4d8d6b803","tid":728804,"uid":156376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:51:40.000Z","msg":"好撚短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e966b8e061a7d8382d47e1af778c6